3
00:00:34,464 --> 00:00:35,159
Are you okay?

4
00:00:36,960 --> 00:00:37,799
Are you hurt?

5
00:00:48,159 --> 00:00:49,600
Should I call you K

6
00:00:51,200 --> 00:00:52,280
or Song Qian?

7
00:00:55,232 --> 00:00:56,384
What are you talking about?

8
00:01:01,439 --> 00:01:03,759
I pressed it
when I was in danger just now.

9
00:01:04,840 --> 00:01:07,519
The person who knew I was in danger
and would come to save me

10
00:01:08,200 --> 00:01:09,439
would only be K.

11
00:01:09,760 --> 00:01:10,799
Because you said,

12
00:01:12,439 --> 00:01:13,599
"If you press it..."

13
00:01:13,760 --> 00:01:14,760
If you press it...

14
00:01:15,719 --> 00:01:16,719
"I'll go to save you."

15
00:01:17,319 --> 00:01:18,400
I'll go to save you.

16
00:01:36,159 --> 00:01:36,879
Why?

17
00:01:38,560 --> 00:01:40,159
