behind all these murders.

24
00:02:11,639 --> 00:02:13,319
Yet, you choose to remain silent.

25
00:02:14,680 --> 00:02:16,960
You'd rather hurt me
to protect them, right?

26
00:02:16,960 --> 00:02:20,800
♪You overturned the story's ending♪

27
00:02:21,824 --> 00:02:23,800
♪Love ultimately becomes regret♪

28
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:26,319
I thought you
had some genuine feelings for me.

29
00:02:28,120 --> 00:02:29,376
I guess I was wrong.

30
00:02:29,690 --> 00:02:32,760
♪Without your company♪

31
00:02:33,728 --> 00:02:35,840
We were never on the same side.

32
00:02:37,479 --> 00:02:38,280
Rest assured.

33
00:02:39,719 --> 00:02:42,039
I won't reveal your identity.

34
00:02:43,319 --> 00:02:44,879
Consider it repaying you for saving me.

35
00:02:46,319 --> 00:02:47,680
I don't owe you anything anymore.

36
00:02:48,416 --> 00:02:50,429
