for the medical seminar?

84
00:06:46,879 --> 00:06:48,199
Sorry, miss,

85
00:06:48,199 --> 00:06:50,199
but we only have
one king room available now.

86
00:06:54,199 --> 00:06:55,000
Qian,

87
00:06:55,360 --> 00:06:57,079
luckily we booked a suite.

88
00:06:57,079 --> 00:06:59,560
