106
00:08:36,759 --> 00:08:38,279
Did you open Zhou Shen's laptop?

107
00:08:38,720 --> 00:08:39,440
I did.

108
00:08:39,919 --> 00:08:41,480
But his office laptop is really clean.

109
00:08:41,840 --> 00:08:43,000
