110
00:08:43,759 --> 00:08:44,720
Impossible.

111
00:08:53,341 --> 00:08:55,039
(Clinic Prescription)

112
00:08:55,039 --> 00:08:57,679
(The hospital prohibits
prescribing these drugs together.)

113
