218
00:16:21,759 --> 00:16:22,960
What do you mean by nothing?

219
00:16:24,840 --> 00:16:26,039
You said you loved me.

220
00:16:26,039 --> 00:16:27,039
That was in the past.

221
00:16:30,639 --> 00:16:32,240
Now, whether you're K

222
00:16:33,080 --> 00:16:34,919
or Song Qian,

223
00:16:35,279 --> 00:16:36,799
I won't love you anymore.

224
00:16:58,639 --> 00:16:59,240
Nian.

225
00:17:38,038 --> 00:17:42,573
♪What is secretly stirring♪

226
00:17:43,862 --> 00:17:48,249
♪From your mouth,
I find it hard to describe♪

227
00:17:49,462 --> 00:17:54,013
♪What praises can disappear
in just a second♪

228
00:17:54,294 --> 00:18:00,448
♪Vanishing without a trace♪

229
00:18:00,918 --> 00:18:06,048
♪Waving hands to break free
from the splendid cage♪

230
00:18:06,518 --> 00:18:11,939
♪Words against the heart,
a pain slashes through the sky♪

231
00:18:12,150 --> 00:18:16,736
♪Floating into the endless night sky,
the wind fierce and strong♪

232
00:18:17,078 --> 00:18:23,901
♪Who is reckless, continuing
to lose control, with impunity♪

233
00:18:25,686 --> 00:18:31,278
♪Let me disappear into the darkness♪

234
00:18:31,510 --> 00:18:36,772
♪Cannot see
who is pulling the strings behind♪

235
00:18:37,174 --> 00:18:41,617
♪The wound still aches,
and the memory is not yet over♪

236
00:18:41,846 --> 00:18:48,139
♪There are two endings,
whether you understand or not♪

237
00:18:48,374 --> 00:18:53,744
♪Let me disappear into the darkness♪

238
00:18:53,974 --> 00:18:59,305
♪Cannot see who is tracking from behind♪

239
00:18:59,606 --> 00:19:04,256
♪The heart still beats,
total blood-red before my eyes♪

240
00:19:04,534 --> 00:19:10,445
♪Only one ending remains,
whether it helps or not♪

241
00:19:10,934 --> 00:19:16,630
♪Let me disappear into the darkness♪
